 h15 y169d ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Kindness and tactfulness toward those who oppose. </div><div class="t m1329 x11 h15 y1966 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Verses 1, 2; Matt. 5:44; 1 Peter 2:21-23. </div><div class="t m127 x73 h15 y17a6 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t m43b x5f h15 y17a6 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The memory of what Christ has saved us from </div><div class="t m776 x11 h15 y19eb ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should make us patient and sympathetic with those out </div><div class="t m267 x11 h15 y167e ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of the way. Acts 22: 3, last part; Eph. 2: 1, 4, 5. </div><div class="t m2b6 x73 h15 y81 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m7d5 x5f h15 y81 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Christian is to witness to the personal experi-</div><div class="t m842 x11 h15 y1730 ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ence of the grace of God-&quot;what thou hast seen and </div><div class="t m1315 x11 h15 y19cc ff4 fs1 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">heard.&quot; Acts 22: 15; Luke 8: 39. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
